        "Description": "The first speedrun challenge designed by O2! This challenge takes place in Whittleton Creek. One target found eating at a party, one target next to a politics booth out in the open, one guard who roams the second floor of Cassidy&apos;s house, and a construction worker in the corner of the map. Note, the last target must be killed with a sniper while wearing the secret robe found in the second floor of the baker&apos;s house. Can you get the best time? Good luck!",
